{"tid":1304316,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"網民反對區議員選舉引入確認書制度恐參選人被DQ　選管會暫收逾11萬份書面意見","createTime":"2019-07-10T14:44:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-10T15:15:32.000Z","uid":212626,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a2dd691b8e860f4bf5415a74530bcc8afa2a009b","tid":1304316,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T14:44:17.000Z","msg":"區議員選舉將於今年11月24日舉行，選舉管理委員會早前就「區議會選舉活動建議指引」進行公眾諮詢將於今晚(10日)結束，其中一項修訂包括引入跟立法會選舉相同的「確認書」制度，即選舉主任有權DQ參選人，引起網民群起反對。選管會回覆本報查詢指，截至今日(10日)上午，已收到約11.2萬份書面申述。<br />\n<br />\n對於網上流傳經「生產器」送出的電郵提供意見不受理，選管會澄清，不論是經郵寄、傳真、電郵(包括經生產器送出)或親身遞交的所有申述，選管會都會仔細考慮。市民如對「區議會選舉活動建議指引」有意見，可於今晚11時59分前電郵至eacenq@eac.hk向選管會提交意見。<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2397023/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2397023%2F&d=RGEj3L6UPYZQbhamDwVV3TXucVKzxOX0ld4zZjK7Pao%3D&h=3ba36058\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2397023/</a>"},{"pid":"e77d218d471346e90a1128ede0e3e04005a81263","tid":1304316,"uid":212626,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T14:45:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>市民如對「區議會選舉活動建議指引」有意見，可於今晚11時59分前電郵至eacenq@eac.hk向選管會提交意見。</strong></span></span><br />\n繼續<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1994cd517be90ab6c73e35f0fa28d9e7bd7b9011","tid":1304316,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T14:46:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5de6f85d8ab3d569eca1d3d4ac442f4df313998d","tid":1304316,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T14:47:24.000Z","msg":"要人呀屌！！！！！！！你班仆街可唔可以生性小小呀！！....<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1304083/page/1?post=1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1304083/page/1?post=1</a>"},{"pid":"6a2c39d38c092bf2e9cbc49ce128d595fb8b1986","tid":1304316,"uid":212